result.adr_address: 93 Lockhart Rd, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 93 Lockhart Rd, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.name: Agave Wanchai

reviews.text:
Delicious Tacos with amazing flavour combinations. We had both of the chef's recommendations, there is some room for improvement for the presentation of the dishes but the taste was very well balanced with fresh ingredients. 

The atmosphere was nice and everything looks very clean. Service was friendly and fast. It was a bit expensive but that is normal in that area.
Great food at a good price! You get free flow drinks and soup for the lunch set  (how about that!) Will definitely be back when I am in Hong Kong.

Excellent Mexican Restaurant! Food and drinks taste amazing. They have a good variety of Tequila to try. The staff is friendly and will always help you. Price level is also good. We will definitely visit this restaurant again.

Great little Mexican joint in the heart of Hong Kong. Good salsa, great tacos, and ice cold Corona! We were looking for a culinary change of pace after two weeks of dim sum, fried rice, and sweet & sour pork...this spot hit the nail on the head.
Good food and atmosphere, can watch the busy street at night.  Extremely expensive for that level/category of restaurant.
